  "page": "Othgar Hoare (the Soulless)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the character with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Othgar_Hoare_(Demonlover)\" title=\"Othgar Hoare (Demonlover)\">Othgar Hoare (Demonlover)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\"><img alt=\"House Hoare 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/50px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/75px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/100px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Othgar Hoare<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Soulless</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\"><img alt=\"House Hoare 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/50px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/75px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/100px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nOthgar Hoare</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"King of the Iron Islands\">King of the Iron Islands</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nOthgar the Soulless</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">House Hoare</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Othgar Hoare</b>, known as <b>Othgar the Soulless</b>, was a <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"King of the Iron Islands\">King of the Iron Islands</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">House Hoare</a>. The Hoare kings of his era were opposed by the priests of the <a href=\"/index.php/Drowned_God\" title=\"Drowned God\">Drowned God</a> because of their support for the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a>, discouraging of reaving, and promotion of trade.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Othgar_Hoare_(the_Soulless)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Iron Islands: The Black Blood.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403212504\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.071 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.267 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 528/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11127/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7216/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 522/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 666/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.62 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  258.720      1 -total\n 86.83%  224.647      1 Template:Infobox_monarch\n 85.98%  222.440      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.77%   33.051     14 Template:Infobox_value\n 10.88%   28.158      1 Template:Hatnote\n  3.26%    8.446      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.67%    4.326      1 Template:Ref\n  0.97%    2.513      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.53%    1.380      1 Template:References\n  0.35%    0.906      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:19021-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403212503 and revision id 295720\n -->\n",
